OL,3,CTeenager who filmed chair being thrown
OL,4,Cin shopping centre pleads guilty
OL,6,FA teenager who filmed another youth
OL,7,Fnarrowly missing shoppers when he
OL,8,Fthrew a sofa from the top floor of a
OL,9,Fshopping centre has admitted
OL,10,Frecklessly causing a public nuisance.
OL,12,FTwo boys were arrested after a viral
OL,13,Fvideo showed the 15kg chair being
OL,14,Flaunched 50ft off the second floor of
OL,15,FWestfield in Stratford, east London,
OL,16,Fas part of an internet prank in March
OL,17,Flast year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
