PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774440171
OL,3,CTeenager who filmed chair being thrown
OL,4,Cin shopping centre pleads guilty
OL,6,FThe boy who threw the chair previously
OL,7,Fadmitted criminal damage and
OL,8,Frecklessly causing a public nuisance,
OL,9,Fand was sentenced to an eight-month
OL,10,Fdetention and training order, the
OL,11,FCrown Prosecution Service (CPS) said.
OL,13,FThe other youth, 15, who filmed the
OL,14,Fvideo, admitted the charges at
OL,15,FStratford Magistrates' Court on Monday
OL,16,Fand he will be sentenced on April 29.
OL,18,FThe footage showed a hooded youth
OL,19,Fthrowing a heavy blue chair over a
OL,20,Fglass balustrade before they run away
OL,21,Fswearing in the opposite direction.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774440171
OL,3,CTeenager who filmed chair being thrown
OL,4,Cin shopping centre pleads guilty
OL,6,FIt was posted online accompanied by
OL,7,Fthe words "No way bro almost killed
OL,8,Fsomeone", the court heard.
OL,10,FProsecutor Elizabeth Ajayi previously
OL,11,Fsaid the chair, which was worth #500,
OL,12,Fwas thrown 50ft from the top floor.
OL,14,FOne of the boys was seen "lifting a
OL,15,Fblue sofa and throwing it over the
OL,16,Fglass balustrade all the way down to
OL,17,Fthe lower floor", she told the court.
OL,19,F"The video went viral," she continued.
