PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1774440171
OL,3,CTeenager who filmed chair being thrown
OL,4,Cin shopping centre pleads guilty
OL,6,F"It's fortunate that nobody was
OL,7,Finjured."
OL,9,FBoth boys admitted their involvement
OL,10,Fin police interviews, she added.
OL,12,FIn a victim impact statement, a
OL,13,FWestfield security officer said there
OL,14,Fhad been "unease" among customers
OL,15,Fsince the incident.
OL,17,FThe boy who threw the chair told
OL,18,Fpolice "it's not that deep, it did not
OL,19,Fhit no-one", the prosecutor added.
