OL,3,CTeenager who filmed chair being thrown
OL,4,Cin shopping centre pleads guilty
OL,6,FHe also told officers he and his co-
OL,7,Fdefendant "regularly indulge" in
OL,8,Fpranks, including "throwing objects
OL,9,Foff bridges at trains", Ms Ajayi said.
